he died in Florida.

00:03:40.720 --> 00:03:43.696
If you want me to study him,
you're going to have to figure out

00:03:43.720 --> 00:03:45.736
how to get me the brain."

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:47.976
So I said, "OK.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:50.720
